The team dropped the Origin Axie presale -- selling the first Axie characte=
rs as NFTs -- in February 2018, raising 900 ETH, just as the price of ETH w=
as beginning to crash off all-time-highs. As ETH fell, they shipped:=C2=A0
In March, they launched their own NFT Marketplace where Axie collectors cou=
ld trade.
In May, they released Breeding, allowing players to combine Axies to make n=
ew ones.
In October, players could battle their Axies.
In January 2019, they raised 3,200 ETH by selling land in Lunacia [https://=
email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE1uxCAMhU8zLCN-QkIWLLqZayACJoOGQESctrl9yWRRyb=
